Input gene information

Completed on Wed Mar 08 15:52:21 2023 (Asia/Shanghai), with the runtime of 3 seconds.

An interactive table for user-input genes (n=304, being processed). The table includes two columns: 1st column Genes for gene symbols, and 2nd column Description for gene description. Each gene listed in the column Genes is hyperlinked to its corresponding GeneCards page.

Output: enriched terms

An interactive table that displays enriched ontology terms. Each enriched term (the columns Ontology, Term ID, and Term Name) has the enrichment Z-score (Z-score), the significance level of the enrichment (FDR), odds ratio (Odds ratio) and 95% confidence intervals (95% CI), the number (Num) and list (Members) of member genes that overlap with your input genes. The table is sorted by FDR ascendingly.

Output: dotplot

A dotplot of enriched ontology terms identified using Fishers exact test. An editable pdf file is also available for download.
